 ，我覺喺咪你無努力過然後就話自己係數理人嚟俾藉口自己懶？<br />\n你覺數學science唔洗背會輕鬆？</blockquote><br />\n我都有諗過尼2個問題。<br />\n我第一個sem 其實都有日日去溫下，但個成績最後都係咁樣既時候，我覺得好難再咁落去。數學science唔係唔洗背，只係可以去理解點解會出現一條式姐。"},{"pid":"fc5fd87496331c9f296c380a051222d32d504304","tid":136290,"uid":24162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"龍仔食唔食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625d5a6c752c66436e3048a0bd58fe6110b5d477","tid":136290,"uid":58384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍仔食唔食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食啦，今朝食左個好豐富既早餐，仲未肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2f428c21380e080693cec6581271e1262e98d","tid":136290,"uid":24162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"等陣仲有冇堂啊"}]}